 decided oneday in spring that I wan=\r\nted to spend the coming Saturday meditating with the Gayatri mantra for the=\r\n whole day. I got that intention from nowhere and did not look at anything =\r\nlike tithi, my horoscope etc. I simply decided to go ahead. I mentioned it =\r\nto Manish and he said, &quot;excellent, go ahead&quot;. I meditated with Gayatri mant=\r\nra from 5 am till\n 9:30 pm, getting up only a few times for 2-minute breaks=\r\n and having a fistful of saattwik food for lunch in the middle of the day. =\r\nWhen I finished in the night, I was in a nice state.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Next morning, I=\r\n realized that the previous day was Akshaya Tritiya (Vaisakha Sukla Tritiya=\r\n, birthday of Ganga and Parasurama and the day Tretayuga started). It is sa=\r\nid that spiritual sadhana done on Akshaya Tritiya is 1,000 times more effec=\r\ntive than a normal day. I was excited that the day I picked at random happe=\r\nned to be an auspicious day.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;I mentioned it to Manish. He said, &quot;I k=\r\nnew it was Akshaya Tritiya even when you mentioned the intention to me&quot;. I =\r\nasked him why he did not tell that to me then. He curtly remarked, &quot;knowing=\r\n you were doing this sadhana on Akshaya Tritiya would not have helped and w=\r\nould have instead distracted you.&quot;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;He was right. As such, I was a li=\r\nttle &quot;proud&quot; of the sadhana - spending the whole day in japam. There was a =\r\nbit of\n excitement and expectancy that was present as an undercurrent and s=\r\nomewhat distracted my focus on the mantra. Had I known that I was doing it =\r\non a day when sadhana is supposed to be 1,000 times more effective, that un=\r\ndercurrent of useless excitement would&#39;ve been higher and distracted me eve=\r\nn more!&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Bottomline: Thumbrules of all kinds exist. But what really m=\r\natters is the state of your mind. Sometimes, doing a sadhana on an auspicio=\r\nus day can create excitement and expectancy and distract one. Doing the sam=\r\ne sadhana everyday and patiently waiting for it to succeed oneday is perhap=\r\ns a simpler and more foolproof strategy. My 2 cents..&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Best regards,&lt;=\r\nBR&gt;Narasimha&lt;BR&gt;------------ --------- --------- --------- --------- ------=\r\n--- -&lt;BR&gt;Free Jyotish Software, Free Jyotish Lessons, Jyotish Writings,&lt;BR&gt;=\r\n&quot;Do It Yourself&quot; ritual manuals for short Homam and Pitri Tarpana:&lt;BR&gt;&lt;A hr=\r\nef=3D&quot;http://www.vedicastrologer.org/&quot; target=3D_blank\n rel=3Dnofollow&gt;http=\r\n://www.VedicAst rologer.org&lt;/A&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Films that make a difference: &lt;A href=3D=\r\n&quot;http://saraswatifilms.org/&quot; target=3D_blank rel=3Dnofollow&gt;http://Saraswat=\r\niFil ms.org&lt;/A&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Spirituality: &lt;A href=3D&quot;http://groups.yahoo.com/group/v=\r\nedic-wisdom&quot; target=3D_blank rel=3Dnofollow&gt;http://groups. yahoo.com/ group=\r\n/vedic- wisdom&lt;/A&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Jyotish writings: &lt;A href=3D&quot;http://groups.yahoo.com/=\r\ngroup/JyotishWritings&quot; target=3D_blank rel=3Dnofollow&gt;http://groups. yahoo.=\r\ncom/ group/JyotishWri tings&lt;/A&gt;&lt;BR&gt;------------ --------- --------- -------=\r\n-- --------- --------- -&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;---- rajarshi14 &lt;&lt;A href=3D&quot;http://ca.mc=\r\n328.mail.yahoo.com/mc/compose?to=3Drajarshi14%40yahoo.co.in&quot; target=3D_blan=\r\nk rel=3Dnofollow ymailto=3D&quot;mailto:rajarshi14%40yahoo.co.in&quot;&gt;rajarshi14@yah=\r\noo. co.in&lt;/A&gt;&gt; wrote: &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; Dear Ashutosh,&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; =\r\n&gt; Someone told me that at the time of homam agnivas is to be&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt=\r\n; ascertained, i.e. it is at prithvi or AkAsh or pAtAl and homam at\n wrong&lt;=\r\nBR&gt;&gt; &gt; agnivas may give adverse results. Is this true? How agnivas ca=\r\nn be&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; ascertained/ determined and what are the impacts of doing=\r\n homam in&lt;